title: MILF Manor
overview: From cities all across the country, eight confident and strong-minded women leave home for the chance to find love at a paradise destination in TLC's brand-new, love and relationship dating series, MILF MANOR. Although they may be a few years older than the average dating show contestant, these women are not out of practice. Ranging from 40 to 60 years young, this vibrant group brings their unique life experiences to the game. They have decades of dating experience and will use it to find a lasting connection with men half their age. However, nothing can prepare them for a jaw dropping surprise that will greet them at the front door.
